{"tid":58882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港女進化史","createTime":"2016-12-29T07:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T08:27:11.000Z","uid":51323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ae715830d3c69fc829e1363f2065fca95c0eb1","tid":58882,"uid":51323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"港女一出世父母當佢如珠如寶<br />\n2歲開始手拎古池手袋 開始明白名牌比飲奶重要<br />\n5歲識得溝男同學 知道男仔係傻下傻下 易於掌握<br />\n10歲學校小息識得痴男同學包媽咪麵<br />\n15歲拍拖 知道原來阿當夏娃食禁果係好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n20歲叱吒風雲 手下士兵將領過百 <br />\n25歲飛走自己已經拍拖3年男友 轉姣上司 公司內扶搖直上<br />\n30歲就開始怕 想反撻舊男友 但法國班男友s 都拖住件23歲美女<br />\n35歲開始呻無好男人<br />\n40歲開始舉旗單身萬歲<br />\n42歲開始做訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n50歲開始停經更年期 日日搵公司班小鮮肉下屬要當佢地公主咁湊<br />\n55歲開始明白自己人又老以經無市場 日日既羨慕又恨羅琳<br />\n60歲進入化境 日日留係屋企睇都市閒情<br />\n70歲入廟堂 與神同遊仙境<br />\n80歲開始去海港城捉細路 迫佢地叫自己做婆婆 叫佢地聽佛經"},{"pid":"d69995badae06b9543b1215c98440bf58f0a9438","tid":58882,"uid":3845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a3a92618d59435e4140ce1092063e340adf85e","tid":58882,"uid":51323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已絕望"},{"pid":"45ce868e31d11db6602c457ff441689f00270b9e","tid":58882,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"麻麻"},{"pid":"000b9b4bb2a9b2fdbbca9f3653f30a99a999523c","tid":58882,"uid":51323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:18:17.000Z","